netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

Class DomainNameGlueRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainNameGlueRecord

  • public class DomainNameGlueRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    A value object used within the Domains API when listing or setting glue records for a domain name. Glue records (sometimes called child nameservers) define explicit mappings of subdomains to IP addresses such that the subdomain may be used as a delegated nameserver for other domains or indeed the domain name itself.
